{"tid":1634182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"( WELL.. )抗爭同選舉其實可以同時做，無矛盾","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T09:16:09.000Z","uid":45206,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"62950aeae93afbbe8b6dbb3b063c2d7226dd71b0","tid":1634182,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:52:00.000Z","msg":"見到陶傑新文章，呼籲大家停止抗爭，全力玩區議會。想回應下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一， 抗爭同選舉無矛盾，兩樣可以同時做。請大家唔好因為區議會，而完全停止抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二，抗爭手法可以討論，但停止就無可能<br />\n<br />\n第三，緊急法已經過咗，政府已經為所欲為。 議會到底有幾大作用，大家心知肚明<br />\n<br />\n第四，陶傑文首&quot; 請不要為林鄭入冊&quot;。但係大家都知道個抗爭其實係為香港，唔係為林鄭。 陶傑係用語言偽術故意將香港改成林鄭， 因為如果句子變做&quot;請不要為香港入冊&quot;就完全講唔通。<br />\n<br />\n陶傑先生我以前都好尊重你，但而家唔得。係咁，再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3e8cf0444cf2a227d3ce6ead9db04ec6711d62","tid":1634182,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:53:22.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3b549ad825b205aac1c5b1834fdc6ac2b172f266","tid":1634182,"uid":265646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"下 更加唔應該為香港入冊啦 入咗冊仲邊個幫香港革命"},{"pid":"57a676ad2f773fc03b06cf62aaeaf2a89b19547a","tid":1634182,"uid":187664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:57:16.000Z","msg":"無論有無暴力情況 今屆選舉都應該9成會延遲"},{"pid":"e6cb716541992a395db5f61e80c078d1a3654c08","tid":1634182,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b549ad825b205aac1c5b1834fdc6ac2b172f266","tid":1634182,"uid":265646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"下 更加唔應該為香港入冊啦 入咗冊仲邊個幫香港革命"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"咁你認同停止所有抗爭？"},{"pid":"7f168eafe2ae6e0ced4d3fec173a7c42e51d65a8","tid":1634182,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:02:53.000Z","msg":"有時唔洗下下硬打既，轉個方式抗爭都得<br />\n比勇武叉叉電 比文宣組做下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631757</a>"},{"pid":"f2d880d7c66745f1844871fc297a78c175095daf","tid":1634182,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57a676ad2f773fc03b06cf62aaeaf2a89b19547a","tid":1634182,"uid":187664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:57:16.000Z","msg":"無論有無暴力情況 今屆選舉都應該9成會延遲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:03:07.000Z","msg":"未必有得選 emergency stage，政府想點就點<br />\n仲想停止抗爭 全力投入選舉"},{"pid":"40fc26ca7f6693f812c3c455d7670a4a08990c1e","tid":1634182,"uid":265646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:03:17.000Z","msg":"抗爭要繼續，重點係抗爭手法、形式。<br />\n文章嘅重點係 tackle fearlessly, not foolishly."},{"pid":"4206a6875d2d51bae5968caa21e1f2216d53b37d","tid":1634182,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:04:36.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<br />\n真係要抗爭嘅話<br />\n係應該要阻止依個不合法 會無故DQ人嘅選舉<br />\n去投票即係代表我哋賦予緊合法性畀政府<br />\n真係要對準政權嘅話<br />\n應該要係票站門口放魔法先啱"},{"pid":"9a83230434f1b569715d5c93c3dec1f1e868d042","tid":1634182,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40fc26ca7f6693f812c3c455d7670a4a08990c1e","tid":1634182,"uid":265646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:03:17.000Z","msg":"抗爭要繼續，重點係抗爭手法、形式。<br />\n文章嘅重點係 tackle fearlessly, not foolishly."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:05:51.000Z","msg":"即係抗爭同選舉可以同時進行，okay<br />\n手法聰唔聰明，同激進程度無關，唔一定要所有激進行為stop，然後重回文宣<br />\n可以討論"},{"pid":"7e64c94788bfc95a082dbae7e99c537cbfb35c37","tid":1634182,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4206a6875d2d51bae5968caa21e1f2216d53b37d","tid":1634182,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:04:36.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<br />\n真係要抗爭嘅話<br />\n係應該要阻止依個不合法 會無故DQ人嘅選舉<br />\n去投票即係代表我哋賦予緊合法性畀政府<br />\n真係要對準政權嘅話<br />\n應該要係票站門口放魔法先啱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:07:50.000Z","msg":"咁又唔好，因爲仲有好多人對選舉有幻想<br />\n無辦法，太多KOL支持選舉，蠱惑人心<br />\n所以我先至想攞個平衡，選舉同抗爭同時進行"},{"pid":"ca1090751c56c58e6cab81059c430bc3c8f9bf05","tid":1634182,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:13:22.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"bb1aeb8f4e2d2530974a3af2362d40fb92eef9ea","tid":1634182,"uid":64159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6cb716541992a395db5f61e80c078d1a3654c08","tid":1634182,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b549ad825b205aac1c5b1834fdc6ac2b172f266","tid":1634182,"uid":265646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"下 更加唔應該為香港入冊啦 入咗冊仲邊個幫香港革命"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"咁你認同停止所有抗爭？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:03:03.000Z","msg":"我估佢係話做咩都好，<br />\n最好都係唔好被狗拉到啫"},{"pid":"511d547d0a856cc7e41389799ac39549eb3e9984","tid":1634182,"uid":294916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:16:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}